dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents buildings for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2010. [The building footprints dataset was developed in 2005 along with the aerial imagery that was flown the same year. The data was created by Ayres in the spring of 2010 with Calumet County adding to the attribute table some time after.]
uw_supplemental_s: This metadata was updated in fall of 2017 to reflect that the data is no longer restricted and has been opened for public use.Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation, please visit http://www.calumetmaps.com/data.html
